cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR

This paper is about image captioning, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning, specifically deep learning. This suggests that cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories. Additionally, the paper involves the generation of natural language descriptions, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
